    "ncContentTypeAlias": "centralBlocks",
    "title": "Withdrawal & Deferral ",
    "content": "<div class=\"page\">\n<div class=\"section\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p><span class=\"lead\">How to Withdraw</span></p>\n<p>If you decide to leave, you will need to complete a <a href=\"/current-students/thinking-of-leaving/forms-and-documents/\" title=\"QMU Withdrawal Form\">withdrawal form</a>. This is used to formally record your withdrawal and update your student record. The date of withdrawal is recorded as the date the form is submitted. This can be important if you receive any funding for your programme or pay any fees.</p>\n<p>You can complete the form electronically and return it to <a href=\"mailto:thinkingofleaving@qmu.ac.uk\" title=\"QMU thinking of leaving\">thinking of leaving email address</a></p>\n<p>Remember to save a copy of the form on your computer first before filling it in.</p>\n<p>A member of staff of the Registry will then update your student record. The Programme Leader, the School Office and any other relevant departments are notified.</p>\n<p><span class=\"lead\">Take a Break from Study (Deferral)</span></p>\n<p>Students can submit a request to defer their studies. This means leaving the programme and returning at a later date, normally the start of the next academic year. Deferrals must be approved by the Programme Leader and are normally granted for a maximum period of 12 months.</p>\n<p>If you decide to apply for a deferral you should read the <a href=\"/about-the-university/quality/committees-regulations-policies-and-procedures/regulations-policies-and-procedures/withdrawal-deferral/\" title=\"QMU Student Deferral Website\">Student Deferral Procedure</a> and discuss your request with your Programme Leader. Once you have done this, you should complete the Deferral Request Form. Remember to save a copy of the form on your computer first before filling it in.</p>\n<p>If you have any questions about the withdrawal or deferral process you can also contact the <a href=\"mailto:thinkingofleaving@qmu.ac.uk\" title=\"QMU thinking of leaving\">thinking of leaving team</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
  }
]]]></Value>
